<h3 id="important-exception">Important Exception</h3>

<hr />

<p>We must be careful not to trigger the fetching state when the <em>data is invalid</em></p>

<p><img src="/images/loading-vs-fetching/facebook-messenger.jpeg" alt="Facebook Messenger Concept" /> Facebook Messenger Concept (Credit: Christoffer O. Jensen)</p>

<p>In this example. Moving between chats should always render the data on the screen invalid.</p>
